Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美红  英语作业借我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有留作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天感冒请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  我可是指望美红的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  土宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做英语作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  能借来看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫同学  也借我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  是邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  医院来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫的妈妈在住院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  你家烦心事这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:00:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本子放在这就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真匆忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课叫你出来不好意思啊  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都对老师撒谎真过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留着口水的痕迹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神乐怪脸收藏又多了一张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种收藏最好删了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N任务之大义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得最近超自然灾害增加了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  恶灵出现次数有些多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉寂了一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有三年没出现这现象了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一根Pocky归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手快者得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴快者得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  有什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴里喊着不要也是喜欢的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉这个色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别往这边看  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天对不起了  上课时还把你们叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的使命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们  被大叔看就无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩端先生是那方面的喜好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面的就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  樱庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…臀部长得不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别拿那种眼神看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐正在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类型B  土蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可是巨无霸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鵺迅速解决掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之  让管狐退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  请往后退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是后方支援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你独担重任还太早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你把舞蹴拾贰号运用自如了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经驾轻就熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那让我见识一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始掩护黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲  弄碎它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通市民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到刚才的东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用拐弯抹角了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是环境省超自然灾害对策室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是消除恶灵的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵感强的人容易被恶灵盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的甚至有无法成佛而自身却变成恶灵的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别再靠近这种地方为好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里所见的千万别向外透露一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你写份誓约书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻生可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我暂时帮你收着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐说这附近已经没有恶灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  状况解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道那女人想自杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全凭经验喽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积累经验多了自然就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了便当  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫啊  你妈妈的病很严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你真了不起啊  还认真完成了作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍稍忙了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为工作几乎不怎么回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在寄宿在亲戚家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是超不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能和亲戚家的姐姐玩又能帮忙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…亲戚家的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  你在打工了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是见习中  帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  能工作就很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀的保养请使用山茶油或丁香油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是日本人的爱刀之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这  你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  家里来了个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  是迈克尔师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来看我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉啊  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快问好啊  这样很失礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是土宫神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土宫大人的女儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是迈克尔小原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔小原不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是打造这把刀的著名刀匠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹴拾贰号  居然是他造的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策室的装备也是迈克尔师傅制作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在问你为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀身闪闪发光  跟新的一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为都不怎么让我作战嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了对神乐来说还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我看下狮子王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这仍是把好刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绽放着强大灵力的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时看来就这么让人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵力消耗得过多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该重新打磨一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子王被拿去打磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就要在没有灵兽的情况下战斗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都要精心照顾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能召唤灵兽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来  这种时候就方便多了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过爸爸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不定时回家见见他的话他会感到很孤单的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家没关系的  就算回了也没人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  我添麻烦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆当我家孩子算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  迈克尔师傅来过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  好像是要暂时保管狮子王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有想给对策室里需要维修的退魔武器进行保养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就一起麻烦他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？那样的话紧急情况发生时装备就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该让她担任主要战斗力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么训练能比得上实战的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  一直依赖小乱也不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拣日不如撞日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把轮班调整下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我会去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人为什么一直都不穿衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死了了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大叔还是这么累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身打扮还真亏他不会被抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔还是会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近段时间可以稍稍休息下了  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是没了狮子王就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩端先生  让我看看退魔装备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本都拿去维修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的话用这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是电熨斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式铁拳打杯28号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（打杯28号：退魔式铁拳。迈克尔小原制作的退魔武器、通过打击对灵体产生破坏。）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用灵水蒸汽外加铁拳  把恶灵打得满地找牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能看上眼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式链锯  PARE  11号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式凿岩机  JACKSON  33号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式锅炉  J.FOX  55号这些而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都差那么点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这么重怎么拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之  陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天有预约了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫某人一直在输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  用这个去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不陪谏山好吗  毕竟是未婚妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让我去讨好父母决定的对象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是毫无感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来说照顾现在这个「女儿」就够受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不去打扰为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20的三倍区  中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾得那么无微不至  真像个「母亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就要定下妻子啊女儿什么的  也真够受的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是15病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（15病：飞镖瞄准20却射中1和5的情况）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才趁现在多玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒无所谓  但别每次都拿我当挡箭牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会被谏山憎恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她憎恨那可是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  的确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的有威力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔师傅造的武器可是很优秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据使用者的灵力  其威力也可以提升数倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐的舞蹴拾贰号也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇形怪状的也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那人是位艺术家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对策室来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（有封新邮件）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是灵力分布出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前银座线的新桥站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在似乎是作为夜晚停车库和休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去碰输电轨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会触电而死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近恶灵出没真频繁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶气若是积攒起来  被召唤的恶灵就会聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶气更是愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样恶性循环下去  就成恶灵的聚集之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初恶气生成一定存在某些原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还蛮好用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类型C  天井尝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢混凝土的污垢的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵水用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果然不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类型D  恶灵化的人类亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那个人已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是曾经是人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成怨灵的灵只能净化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍下去  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们退魔师的使命就是驱除在人世间散布死亡污秽之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰灵解放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫家代代相传最强的灵兽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰灵  白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道出生在退魔师家所应担负的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道这份责任有多重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不断修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:26.40,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:37.08,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:47.80,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.79,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:23:00.39,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.79,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:11.06,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:26.55,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:26.40,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经对自己的心灵　许下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:37.08,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救赎　卷入叹息漩涡中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:47.80,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交错的时光转瞬即逝　道理的齿轮锈迹斑斓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.79,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已经无法后退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:23:00.39,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毁一切　亦无容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.79,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:11.06,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将那时仅有的幸福　深情拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:26.55,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}将远去的梦的足音　刻骨铭心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话  喰霊  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执念


